{"tid":2200512,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有連登巴絲係蘋果落廣告","createTime":"2020-09-13T04:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T09:12:44.000Z","uid":5021,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8e33efbf8315dfa57264dd2820bcc083d7b56b2a","tid":2200512,"uid":5021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"第二次係蘋果落廣告, 今次係同4位唔同既巴絲夾份登報<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddwp2PV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fddwp2PV.png&h=50f5df86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuRYnPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuRYnPY.jpg&h=bd8fa7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係度想同大家講, 如果大家都想支持蘋果其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以試下好似我地咁係蘋果落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實真係無想像中咁貴, 我地咁樣一人一格都係除番開$1250一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果學生無咁多資金, 亦都可以試下落分類廣告留一兩句自己想表達既文字都係<br />\n$90一格, 絕對係一個除左訂閱/買報紙之外既好方法去Support蘋果! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣請透過以下方法聯絡蘋果職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LFqNgR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LFqNgR.png&h=9723451f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程好簡單, 先取報價單, 然後講清楚自己想落邊類型既廣告<br />\n然後就按要求整好份圖再Email份稿比蘋果<br />\n佢地對完 OK既 就會叫你比錢同簽名, 之後等2日左右就會成功登報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------</strong><br />\n回到正題<br />\n希望大家可以支持小弟開既Youtube Channel<br />\nChannel以前主要係分享一些旅遊影片, 剛開始拍片所以拍攝同剪片技巧都唔係太好, <br />\n但會繼續努力改善同學習!<br />\n而將來主要會分享在日本生活的影片<br />\n包括日本留學生活, 及將來係日本創業申請經營管理簽證等過程, <br />\n都會想同大家分享!<br />\n如無意外年尾會出發 <br />\n只求訂閱 多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Youtube Channel: Kiu &amp; Chung</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnMydi5m1GAj96zt59K3M-g?sub_confirmation=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCnMydi5m1GAj96zt59K3M-g%3Fsub_confirmation%3D1&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513cFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=0cd4d9b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnMydi5m1GAj96zt59K3M-g?sub_confirmation=1</a><br />\n <strong>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------</strong><br />\n之前以為係蘋果落廣告普通人負擔唔起, 但其實唔係<br />\n平有平落, 貴有貴落, 唔係一定下下落頭條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家都可以試下, 出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果關於落廣告方面 有唔明既地方都可以係下面問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6a84d7bb5d3cf8eb11dfd9d6553fcd91302a59","tid":2200512,"uid":5021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"希望蘋果落廣告熱潮唔係三分鐘熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678d16f26bdaaf6af4e734f6678d810ddce5123d","tid":2200512,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26c507bfbdecfcee8860488fac36f771a6021899","tid":2200512,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"push ar"},{"pid":"4014fde228e10f6e5387a896af04b8d1ae4304ce","tid":2200512,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"wow push"},{"pid":"c6724c6f53d599a1571b731c82f5d98b5be59206","tid":2200512,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />